Package: cohort
Title: Cohort Construction with Provenance
Version: 2026.5.10
Authors@R: c(
  person(c("Richard","Aubrey"), "White", email = "hello@rwhite.no", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6747-1726"))
  )
Description: A framework for building analytic cohorts with full provenance.
    Supports branched cohort trees, per-step exclusion logging with
    human-readable reasons, schema validation at branch boundaries, cached
    derived artifacts on each cohort, and CONSORT diagram generation. Designed
    to feed analytic data tables into downstream orchestration packages such
    as 'plnr', the framework cleanly separates cohort definition from
    analysis. A shared-base storage strategy keeps memory flat as the cohort
    tree grows.
